com.jme3.material

Class ShaderGenerationInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme3.material.ShaderGenerationInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Savable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class ShaderGenerationInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements Savable, java.lang.Cloneable
    this class is basically a struct that contains the ShaderNodes informations in an appropriate way to ease the shader generation process and make it faster.
